children.name: Tom_Intro
children.label: Introduction to the Sustainabl...
children.description:
Introduction to the Sustainable 
Supply Chain 
Maturity Report 

In the interconnected 
world of global 
commerce, the 
supply chain is 
not just a logistical operation; it is the backbone of organizational sustainability. 
Since the early 2000s, I have been deeply embedded in the evolution of supply 
chainsâ€”from 
pioneering 
SaaS-delivered 
reverse logistics applications to 
advancing sustainability practices within 
major corporations. 
My tenure as a 
VP at SAP and 
my ongoing 
engagement 
through over 
500 episodes 
of the Sustainable 
Supply Chain and 
Climate Confident podcasts have afforded me a unique vantage point on the critical intersection of supply chain management and sustainability efforts.

Introduction to the Sustainable 
Supply Chain 
Maturity Report 

In the interconnected 
world of global 
commerce, the 
supply chain is 
not just a logistical operation; it is the backbone of organizational sustainability. 
Since the early 2000s, I have been deeply embedded in the evolution of supply 
chainsâ€”from 
pioneering 
SaaS-delivered 
reverse logistics applications to 
advancing sustainability practices within 
major corporations. 
My tenure as a 
VP at SAP and 
my ongoing 
engagement 
through over 
500 episodes 
of the Sustainable 
Supply Chain and 
Climate Confident podcasts have afforded me a unique vantage point on the critical intersection of supply chain management and sustainability efforts.
